  "bms": {
    "type_detection": "NONE in power. _panasonic/_dynapack/_liteon_* are static-init device-firmware-name fragments (registry built by main + _INIT_7/11/12 via std::string ctor 0x112100 + operator+ 0x111fb0); all registered unconditionally, no runtime vendor/chemistry branch. Supplier ID is a FOTA/version-matching concern (update service / BMS firmware), not sensed here.",
